quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  38,84,"Allah said: the truth is, and it is the truth that I speak"
  38,85,"That I shall fill Hell with thee and such of them as shall follow thee, all together"
  38,86,"Say thou: ask of you for it no hire, nor am I of the affecters"
  38,87,It is naught but an admonition Unto the worlds
  38,88,And ye shall surely come to know the truth thereof after a season
  39,1,"The revelation of this Book is from Allah, the Mighty, the Wise"
  39,2,"Verily We! We have sent down the Book Unto thee With truth: wherefore worship thou Allah, making exclusion for Him in religion"
  39,3,"LO! for Allah is the religion exclusive. And those who take patrons beside Him, saying: We Worship them not save in order that they may bring us nigh Unto God in approach - -verily Allah will judge between them concerning that wherein they differ. Verily Allah guideth not him who is a liar and ingrate"
  39,4,"Had Allah willed to take a son, He could have chosen whatsoever He pleased out of that which He hath created. Hallowed be He! He is Allah the One, the Subduer"
  39,5,"He hath created the heavens and the earth with truth. He rolleth the night around the day, and rolleth the day around the night, and He hath subjected the sun and the moon: each running on for a term appointed! Lo! He is the Mighty, the Forgiver"